spx.packets.tracks

Class Fusion

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.tracks.Fusion

  • public class Fusion
extends java.lang.Object
    Fusion information.

    The Fusion structure is contained within the extended track report structure.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketTrackFusion structure in "SPxPackets.h".

    See Also:
    Extended

    • Field Detail

      • sensorTypes

        public long sensorTypes
        Sensor types.

        The sensorTypes field is set to a combination of values from the Sensor interface.

        See Also:
        Sensor

      • sensors

        public long sensors
        Sensors.

        Bitmap of which sensors are supporting the track. LSB is sensor 0, etc. Up to 32 sensors can be included.

      • trackID

        public long[] trackID
        Array of track IDs.

        This allows a receiver to interact with the originating server to get or set information for, or delete, tracks, The number of entries in this array corresponds to the number of bits set in sensors; trackId[0] corresponds to the least significant bit set and so on.

      • maxRangeDiffMetres

        public float maxRangeDiffMetres
        Maximum range difference.

        The maximum separation in metres between any two observations contributing to this track.

      • reserved

        public byte[] reserved
        Reserved for future use.
